{"tid":1411880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問題係堵路呀！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T04:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T10:56:18.000Z","uid":76543,"like":22,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e614a756cf86cd9dac9ec75d90d099df82be5646","tid":1411880,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯 白車到我哋一定讓 會開路 但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白車係中間塞死</span></span>你點讓呀！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>地鐵不合作運動我絕對支持</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好封路</strong></span></span> 唔好癱瘓全港交通<br />\n咁樣到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真正有需要嘅人士</strong></span></span>要白車 緊急去醫院咁 塞死咗點算<br />\n可能cctvb話咩大肚婆係fake news都好 咁如果真係發生呢 白車真係會塞死喎<br />\n手足要救援呢 白車嚟唔到又點算<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好互屌 係想一齊討論</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋慢慢進步 每次都檢討 考慮多啲<br />\n希望下一次可以做得更好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"64c583d128a493d7138ef388adba5c25d1c81afc","tid":1411880,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8455d06ed9fba65ccbc47a2ee5b3287434708ec4","tid":1411880,"uid":76543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"留番啲路俾真正有需要嘅人士"},{"pid":"f2f1cc3f5861f56fca169f4d30e78a3b1afba913","tid":1411880,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:50:57.000Z","msg":"無必要全封"},{"pid":"07d64